    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cat Snap – a cozy puzzle game about capturing adorable moments!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide a free-spirited kitty around each level and snap the perfect moment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play with the kitty in all kinds of scenes</strong><br>Interact with the cat as it wanders, plays, and reacts to different situations, then catch the moment with your camera!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique cat behavior in every level</strong><br>Each stage features different movements and playful antics. Try new ways to guide the kitty and discover cute poses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take photos</strong><br>Capture one or more photos per level and collect your favorite memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photo Album</strong><br>Browse every picture you've taken and look back on your adorable moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Specs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: <strong>About 30 minutes</strong></p>",
